<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink119">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi naṉṟu</l>
<l>meyyā maiyi ṉētila paṟṟi</l>
<l>yaṉpilaṉ maṉṟa peritē</l>
<l>meṉpulak koṇkaṉ vārā tōṉē</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Oh friend, listen!</l>
<l>The man from the shore with soft lands who did not come,</l>
<l>Having grasped strange ways due to his great ignorance,</l>
<l>Is very much without love.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
